---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
import Title from "../shared/Title.astro";
---

<section id="features" class="relative pt-24 pb-24 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-32 bg-[#4f46e5]">
    <Container className="flex flex-col midmd:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12">
        
        <div class="flex-1 flex midmd:w-7/12 lg:w-1/2 flex-col">
            <h2><Title class="text-white">
                Estrategia de social media
            </Title></h2>
            <Paragraph className="mt-2 text-white">
               -----------------------------------------------------------
            </Paragraph>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1 flex midmd:w-7/12 lg:w-1/2 flex-col">
            <Paragraph className="mt-8 text-white  text-lg lg:text-xl">
                Una estrategia de social media efectiva potencia tu marca, aumenta la visibilidad y genera leads cualificados. Optimiza tu presencia en redes y alcanza tus objetivos de marketing.
                <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-heading-3 font-medium text-white text-lg lg:text-xl">
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Asesoría, contenido y estrategia de redes sociales

                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Producción de vídeo y fotografía


                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Estrategia de comunicación
 


                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Informes y analíticas



                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Diseño de newsletters

                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center">&checkmark;</span> Cobertura de eventos

                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-8">
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>